   "source": [
    "# Wavenumber Spectra"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "479de3b2-f27a-400f-bddb-c24e81fcc938",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import sys, os, shutil, io\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from functools import partial\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import pandas as pd \n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "935db7e9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df_27  = pd.read_csv('../results/wavenumberspectra_Z027.csv')\n",
    "df_90  = pd.read_csv('../results/wavenumberspectra_Z090.csv')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "ebfa0ed8",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ustar = 0.468587\n",
    "zi = 803.132957\n",
    "a1d = 0.5\n",
    "ah = 0.54 * (55/18) * a1d"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "213bba0e",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 2000x750 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Run the driver\n",
    "fsize = 18\n",
    "s=12\n",
    "dfs = [df_27,df_90]\n",
    "fig, axs = plt.subplots(1,len(dfs),figsize=(8*len(dfs),6), dpi=125, sharey=True)\n",
    "zs = [27,90,]\n",
    "fact = [0.0025,0.0015,]\n",
    "for axiter, ax in enumerate(axs):\n",
    "    plt.sca(ax)\n",
    "    df = dfs[axiter]\n",
    "    normz = zs[axiter]/zi\n",
    "    strz = f\"{normz:.2f}\"\n",
    "    ax.set_title('z = '+str(zs[axiter])+'m ($z/z_i$ = ' + strz + ')',fontsize=fsize)\n",
    "    Escaling =  2 * np.pi / (zi * ustar**2 * ah) \n",
    "    kscaling = zi\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.xticks(fontsize=fsize)  # Set x tick label font size\n",
    "    plt.yticks(fontsize=fsize)  # Set y tick label font size\n",
    "\n",
    "    msize = 5\n",
    "    plt.loglog(kscaling * df['kmag'],fact[axiter]*df['kmag']**(-5/3),c='tab:gray',ls='-',label='$k^{-5/3}$')\n",
    "    plt.loglog(kscaling * df['kmag'],Escaling * df['energy'],c='tab:blue',label='Energy spectra\\nAMR-Wind',marker='o',markersize=msize,ls='-')\n",
    "    plt.loglog(kscaling * df['kmag'],Escaling * df['horiz'],c='tab:red',label='Horizontal spectra\\nAMR-Wind',marker='D',markersize=msize,ls='-.')\n",
    "    plt.loglog(kscaling * df['kmag'],Escaling * df['vertical'],c='tab:green',label='Vertical spectra\\nAMR-Wind',marker='s',markersize=msize,ls='--')\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.ylabel(\"$\\\\alpha_h^{-1} E(\\kappa_h)2\\pi/z_i u_*^2$\",fontsize =fsize)\n",
    "    plt.xlabel(\"$\\kappa_h z_i$\",fontsize=fsize)\n",
    "    if axiter == len(dfs)-1:\n",
    "        plt.legend(loc=4,fontsize=fsize-4,bbox_to_anchor=(1.5,0.55))\n",
    "\n",
    "    ax.set_xlim(1,500)\n",
    "    ax.set_ylim(0.001,3)\n",
    "plt.savefig(\"./figures/ABL_wavenumber_spectra.png\")\n"
   ]
  },
